		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://en.blog.wordpress.com/?p=41531</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[We’ve added four new color schemes to customize your WordPress.com dashboard!]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>We heard you: You want bolder and brighter colors on WordPress.com. Today we&#8217;re bringing your WordPress.com dashboard to life with four new color schemes: introducing Midnight, Sunset, Ocean, and Contrast.</p>



<p>You may recognize some of these colors as old friends. Midnight, Sunset, and Ocean are based on early versions of WordPress — a nod to our roots as we evolve:</p>



<ul data-carousel-extra='{"blog_id":3584907,"permalink":"https:\/\/en.blog.wordpress.com\/2019\/07\/24\/four-new-wordpress-com-color-schemes\/"}' class="wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped"><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img data-attachment-id="41545" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/color-scheme-thumbnail-midnight/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-midnight.png" data-orig-size="1482,988" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-midnight.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-midnight.png?w=720" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=656&type=img" alt="Midnight color scheme" data-id="41545" data-link="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/color-scheme-thumbnail-midnight/" class="wp-image-41545" srcset="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=517&type=img 720w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=657&type=img 1440w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=658&type=img 150w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=659&type=img 300w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=660&type=img 768w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=661&type=img 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img data-attachment-id="41547" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/color-scheme-thumbnail-sunset/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-sunset.png" data-orig-size="1482,988" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-sunset.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-sunset.png?w=720" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=662&type=img" alt="Sunset color scheme" data-id="41547" data-link="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/color-scheme-thumbnail-sunset/" class="wp-image-41547" srcset="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=523&type=img 720w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=663&type=img 1440w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=664&type=img 150w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=665&type=img 300w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=666&type=img 768w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=667&type=img 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></figure></li><li class="blocks-gallery-item"><figure><img data-attachment-id="41546" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/color-scheme-thumbnail-ocean/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-ocean.png" data-orig-size="1482,988" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-ocean.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/color-scheme-thumbnail-ocean.png?w=720" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=668&type=img" alt="Ocean color scheme" data-id="41546" data-link="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/color-scheme-thumbnail-ocean/" class="wp-image-41546" srcset="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=529&type=img 720w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=669&type=img 1440w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=670&type=img 150w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=671&type=img 300w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=672&type=img 768w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=673&type=img 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></figure></li></ul>



<p>If bright and bold isn&#8217;t your jam, you might prefer Contrast, a black-and-white scheme meant to bring your WordPress.com dashboard into sharp focus:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img data-attachment-id="41556" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11-59-13-am/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.59.13-am.png" data-orig-size="2560,1600" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.59.13-am" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.59.13-am.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.59.13-am.png?w=720" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=674&type=img" alt="Screenshot of the WordPress.com dashboard with Contrast color scheme applied." class="wp-image-41556" /></figure>



<p>As part of our commitment to <a href="https://automattic.design/2018/12/22/13429/">inclusive design</a>, the new palettes are optimized for contrast and increased legibility. Whichever color scheme you choose, your dashboard remains stylish and readable.</p>



<h3>Here’s how to customize your color scheme:</h3>



<ol><li>On your desktop, sign in to the WordPress.com account that you’d like to customize.</li><li>Click your account avatar in the upper right corner.</li><li>Select <strong>Account Settings</strong></li><li>Select one of the options under <strong>Dashboard Color Scheme</strong></li><li>Click <strong>Save Account Settings</strong> to apply the change</li></ol>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img data-attachment-id="41555" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11-58-52-am/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.58.52-am.png" data-orig-size="2560,1600" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.58.52-am" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.58.52-am.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/screen-shot-2019-07-17-at-11.58.52-am.png?w=720" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=675&type=img" alt="Screenshot of the WordPress.com Account Settings." class="wp-image-41555" /></figure>
]]></content:encoded>
