		<item>
		<title>More Stats, Better Stats, Faster Stats: A Whole New Mobile Experience</title>
		<link>https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2019/07/16/more-stats-better-stats-faster-stats-a-whole-new-mobile-experience/</link>
				<comments>https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2019/07/16/more-stats-better-stats-faster-stats-a-whole-new-mobile-experience/#comments</comments>
				<pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2019 16:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Sylvester Wilmott]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Mobile]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Stats]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://en.blog.wordpress.com/?p=41452</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[If you’re like me, Stats is one of your most-visited screens in your WordPress app &#8212; we all want to know people are reading! Whether you use iOS or Android, the latest versions have Stat updates that bring you more useful data, faster. Updates to the layout, available statistics, and &#8230;]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>If you’re like me, Stats is one of your most-visited screens in your WordPress app &#8212; we all want to know people are reading! Whether you use iOS or Android, the latest versions have Stat updates that bring you more useful data, faster. Updates to the layout, available statistics, and how they’re handled behind the scenes mean you can hone in what’s most important to you and to your site’s growth.</p>



<h2>What&#8217;s new?</h2>



<hr class="wp-block-separator" />



<div class="wp-block-media-text alignwide is-vertically-aligned-top"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img data-attachment-id="41505" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2019/07/16/more-stats-better-stats-faster-stats-a-whole-new-mobile-experience/stats_countries/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_countries.png" data-orig-size="720,1560" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="stats_countries" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_countries.png?w=138" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_countries.png?w=473" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=676&type=img" alt="" class="wp-image-41505" srcset="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=537&type=img 473w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=677&type=img 69w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=678&type=img 138w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=679&type=img 720w" sizes="(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<h4>All-new design</h4>



<p>Stats got a facelift! The numbers are easier to read, easier to compare, and easier to track over time.</p>
</div></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator" />



<div class="wp-block-media-text alignwide is-vertically-aligned-top"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img data-attachment-id="41481" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2019/07/16/more-stats-better-stats-faster-stats-a-whole-new-mobile-experience/stats_manage-2/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_manage-2.png" data-orig-size="720,1280" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="stats_manage" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_manage-2.png?w=169" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_manage-2.png?w=576" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=680&type=img" alt="" class="wp-image-41481" srcset="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=541&type=img 576w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=681&type=img 84w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=682&type=img 169w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=683&type=img 720w" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<h4>Customise your stats</h4>



<p style="text-align:left;">Blogger who wants to keep an eye on your follower count, a business owner who wants a quick update on daily views? Insights Management lets you choose what stats to include so your at-a-glance updates include what’s most important to you. (This feature is only available on Android at the moment, and is coming soon to iOS.)</p>
</div></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator" />



<div class="wp-block-media-text alignwide is-vertically-aligned-top"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img data-attachment-id="41493" data-permalink="https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2019/07/16/more-stats-better-stats-faster-stats-a-whole-new-mobile-experience/stats_date_bar/" data-orig-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_date_bar-5.png" data-orig-size="720,1560" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="stats_date_bar" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_date_bar-5.png?w=138" data-large-file="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/stats_date_bar-5.png?w=473" src="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=684&type=img" alt="" class="wp-image-41493" srcset="https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=545&type=img 473w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=685&type=img 69w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=686&type=img 138w, https://steemsafe.net:443/php/loadfile.php?fileid=162&index=687&type=img 720w" sizes="(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<h4><strong>Zero in on time periods</strong></h4>



<p>Use the new dedicated date bar on the days, weeks, months and years tabs, to explore date ranges.</p>
</div></div>



<hr class="wp-block-separator" />



