<h2>How do I find this?</h2>



<p>Update your app to the latest version. You can find them <a href="https://apps.wordpress.com/mobile/">here</a>, or in your Apple Store or Google Play. And that’s it! Head to Stats for any of your site for a new and improved analytics experience.</p>



